  {"depth": 2, "slug": "learning-tips", "text": "Tips for Learning Chengyu"}
];
---
<BlogLayout
  title="Chinese Idioms (Chengyu): 30 Essential Four-Character Expressions"
  description="Master 30 essential Chinese chengyu (四字成语) with origin stories, meanings, example sentences, and tips for natural usage. Organized by daily life, stories, study, and business."
